Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.67,0:00:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以摸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋天某一日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了個摸了我的女朋友卜部美琴的胸部的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『謎之感覺』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.93,0:02:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺昨天在夢中所摸到的卜部胸部的觸感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還留在這只右手上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,軟軟的卻很有彈性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸到的時候腦子突然一下麻痹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的卜部的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.91,0:02:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會也是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.98,0:02:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期日大白天就宅在家裏淨想一些沉悶的妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附近的書店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣 吃個肉包子再去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平時都跑過來吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正值青春呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.51,0:03:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是看到肉包子就慌了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐可能會覺得我很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說要抑制了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣都成了反效果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從家裏出來還沒過30分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 接下來到哪去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還是跑來這了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這條路 卜部一直都是從這邊回去來著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部的家就在這前面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這附近沒怎麼來過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部的家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺是這樣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開個玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…你問我為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 跑到我家前面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找我有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏難道是卜部的家？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部 那啥… 買東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 在附近的超市買食材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是隨便散散步而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到會這麼巧碰上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.31,0:05:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得來一次 到我家喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我幫你拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部家是第十層啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過居然能到卜部家去 超幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部 你家裏的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:05:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天只有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部的家人 感覺無法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下來等一等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去泡茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢中的感覺差點甦醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種適合女孩子穿的冬季毛衣 胸部線條會很突出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是對於昨天做了那種夢的我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太過於刺激了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易第一次來到卜部的房間裏 我要振作點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:06:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部的書包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平時的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部的床
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部每晚都在這裏睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺有種卜部的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那啥… 感覺這床會睡得很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我嚇了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿突然出現在我們家的公寓前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨意散散步就到了這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 感覺天突然黑了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道會不會下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果下雨的話 時機就太準了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能在卜部家裏避雨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我有什麼在意的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 沒有什麼在意的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確很多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 做了那種夢之後 偶然兩人獨處就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這或許是上天賜予我的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 這個咖啡味道不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被那雙眼看著的時候 進攻的衝動就會冷卻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來要下一場雨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺雷好近的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開燈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好響啊 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部沒燙傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是咖啡沾了點在腳上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿 想趁亂做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿 對我果然有什麼在意的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天做了個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:10:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…摸了卜部胸部的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的胸部？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那個夢裏的觸感從腦袋裏揮之不去 不由地就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在夢裏摸到的 我的胸部的觸感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是怎樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,軟軟的 很有彈性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸到的時候腦子裏突然一下子麻痹了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和夢裏的觸感相比如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個… 比夢裏的觸感更…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更…更…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼淚…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得用不著哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺突然就掉下來了… 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你希望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接用自己的手來摸也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你希望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接用自己的手來摸也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 這種事我覺得還是顧及雙方的感受比較…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能讓衝動牽著鼻子走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要雙方的感受都好好地…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我數三聲還不摸的話 就當這事沒發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的摸到了卜部的胸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心臟跳得很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,0:12:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個心跳不是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是傳達到我手上的 卜部心臟的跳動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部的耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部的嘴唇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都幹了些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為卜部的話而得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這麼推倒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把卜部 弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個… 卜部 你在生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 沒在生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 最後是宮崎當地雞做的鳥燒燻肉卷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:14:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丘同學 甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜點？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部同學給的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸口好像跳得很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體變得很熱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼鏡起霧了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然以前也有舔了卜部同學的口水後身體變熱的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才舔的和之前的是不同等級的熱度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道卜部同學你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近和椿發生了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與其說最近 應該是昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一些從來沒感受過的奇怪感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種感覺至今為止沒有感受過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今為止沒有感受過的感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.77,0:16:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具體發生了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 會有那種感覺是很普通的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為一旦戀愛了 自己的感覺就會發生變化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的感覺會變化？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是說 和上野交往了之後 丘同學也發生了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點一點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才舔了口水後 那至今為止沒有過的心跳加速就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部心裏更有數吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼鏡又起霧了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是說 那兩人之間發生了很大的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為我走的更遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下可能被超越了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些反應式的實例
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以這樣表示 這裏考試會出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸了卜部的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘我地將她推倒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.07,0:18:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把卜部弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在那種尷尬的氛圍下丟下卜部一個人自己走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為男人太丟臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 昨天我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把卜部弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.87,0:18:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天我不是說了嗎 我沒有在生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的我沒有舔卜部口水的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…在做日課之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:19:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,揍我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你生不生氣的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是我 作為男朋友弄哭了自己女朋友的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去 我會過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以揍我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做日課的話 就在那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打耳光可是很痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 狠狠地來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸摸我的耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耳朵？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再用力點捏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼淚…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:19:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因為你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天被椿做了那樣的事之後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知為什麼耳朵被摸眼淚就會流出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你改變了我的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個感覺我並不討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與其說討厭 不如說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你因為昨天的事情要接受痛苦的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就要接受同樣的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己的耳光可真是痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟說了能摸胸部的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,責任我也有一份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.21,0:20:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部 你這麼說我的確會輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可說實話 希望不要舔我現在的口水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:21:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被揍 在我的臉上留下疤痕是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可在我喜歡的卜部臉上留下傷痕絕對不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 椿今天那份
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過剛才那些話就算是我本人也有點害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你改變了我的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來我們會有很多事發生改變吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第9話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『謎之「總感覺有點…」』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.79,0:23:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部早餐是和式還是洋式？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.94,0:23:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有特地定下來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.62,0:23:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但燻肉卷不會做 因為中午肯定能吃得到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丘的便當？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.30,0:23:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說現在有一百零八種變化
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.86,0:23:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 謎之彼女X 第9話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謎之「總感覺有點…」

